fields.description:
After updating to GreenHopper 6.2.1, the Issue details view is very small.

Looking at the HTML, it looks like the width is set to 400px:

{code:title=batch.css (line 204)}
#ghx-detail-view {
    width: 400px;
}
{code}

Changing 400px to free solves the problem.

Current text:
